word_mean_info__list.difference: 通常指两个或多个物体，特别是金属物发出刺耳声音或破裂声的撞击。也可引申指意见、利益等的冲突。
指物体相撞，其结果不是受损就是严重受阻。
正式用词，侧重指物体相撞的结果或接触点。
指强烈冲击在肉体上或思想感情上所产生的效果。

bilingual.source: Compare the language, style and impact of writing.
bilingual.target: 比较语言、风格和写作的影响。

bilingual.source: The climate change is having a great impact on the environment.
bilingual.target: 气候变化正在给环境带来巨大影响。

bilingual.source: Globalisation has had a huge impact on people all around the world.
bilingual.target: 全球化对世界各地的人们产生了巨大影响。

bilingual.source: This has had a negative impact on the unique plants and animals living there.
bilingual.target: 这对那里的独特植物和动物产生了负面影响。

bilingual.source: It's an honour to be here and to share with you the story of how music has had an impact on my life.
bilingual.target: 很荣幸能在这里与大家分享音乐对我生活的影响。

bilingual.source: Placing stress on particular words can have a big impact on the meaning and strength of apologies.
bilingual.target: 强调特定词语会对道歉的意义和力度产生重大影响。

bilingual.source: Well known as a successful band, the Impact members show quite a few striking abilities.
bilingual.target: 作为一个成功的乐队，影响乐队的成员展示了不少惊人的能力。

bilingual.source: I use my photography to make an impact on people, especially when it comes to environmental issues.
bilingual.target: 我用我的摄影作品对人们产生影响，特别是在环境问题上。

bilingual.source: The impact of the speech was lasting.

list.abstract: Impact，网络营销概念，在科学总结和归纳的基础上，推出了IMPACT网络营销理念，它以“选择决定营销效果”作为理念的核心。同名电影《月殒天劫》。
在2004年6月4日，TNA的TNAiMPACT!在FoxSportsNet播出，它和当时的每周PPV一起成为了TNA的主要收入来源。

yingyinNormal.en: It's about Mr. Spock and his impact on our culture.
yingyinNormal.zh: 主题是史波克先生及他对我们文化的影响。

yingyinNormal.en: So what is Impact 10x10x10?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以什么是影响力10x10x10？
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《艾玛·沃特森达沃斯世界经济论坛HeForShe演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, you keep saying how much Sheldon has affected all of us, but you've clearly had an impact on him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你一直在说谢尔顿对我们的影响有多大，但显然，你也影响了他。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. I think people underestimate the importance of detail to the overall impact. Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊。我觉得人们会低估注重细节对整体感觉的影响。是啊。

yingyinNormal.en: The part of the wire that we're going to today, if that goes down, what happens? What's the impact?
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天我们要去看看线路。要是线路断了，有什么后果？有什么影响？

yingyinNormal.en: Whether we like it or not, in the past 20 years, Internet has launched a huge impact to the human lives.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论你是否喜欢，过去20年，互联网对人类社会产生了巨大的影响。

yingyinNormal.en: A similar impact, or worse, could happen any time and turn our blue marble into a lifeless rock.
yingyinNormal.zh: 类似的影响，或者更糟，随时都可能会发生并把我们的蓝色星球变成无生命之地。

yingyinNormal.en: But the subway has had an even bigger impact than that, starting in the early 1900s, when the first track was laid.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而地铁的影响还不止于此，它起源于20世纪早期，第一条铁路线诞生了。

yingyinNormal.en: The driver's been unreachable since his shift began. There's enough radiation on that truck to impact a 30-mile radius.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自从他的轮班开始，司机就失联了。卡车上的放射物足够影响方圆50公里左右的区域。

yingyinNormal.en: I finally have time to test my hypothesis about the separation of the water molecules from the egg proteins and its impact vis-a-vis taste.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我终于有时间验证我的理论，从蛋白质中分离水分子，以及它对口感的影响。

yingyinNormal.en: But first, let me take you on a journey around China to see some of the real people, real stories that Alibaba has impact on them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过，首先让带您开启一段走遍中国的旅程，看看阿里巴巴对他们产生了什么影响。

yingyinNormal.en: If a player scores a goal, it ultimately has a stronger impact on your impression of their skills than if they miss the net.
yingyinNormal.zh: 足球员射门得分，这最后会有个更强的影响加深你对他们球技的印象，比起他们没有得分的话。

yingyinNormal.en: Kalique is in competition with Balem. She knows that the loss of the earth will reduce his yield and impact his position in the market. His loss is her gain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她和拜蓝有矛盾。他知道失去地球会对拜蓝的产品和市场遭成巨大影响，这叫损人利己。

yingyinNormal.en: That's too bad. I was hoping you could be my plus-one at the Institute of Interdisciplinary Studies' symposium on the impact of current scientific research on societal interactions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真不幸，我还想让你当我的伴儿一起去多学科研究院参加现行科学研究对社会交互的影响研讨会。

yingyinNormal.en: On one hand, learning very negative, highly immoral information about someone typically has a stronger impact than learning very positive, highly moral information.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一方面，知道关于某人非常负面、非常不道德的信息，基本上会有更强的影响，相对于得知某人有非常正面、道德的信息。

yingyinNormal.en: The lockout has a very large impact on a lot of people. The current offer that is on the table s not one that we can accept. It could be a couple weeks, could be a couple months.
yingyinNormal.zh: 停摆对很多人有巨大影响，目前放在谈判桌上的条件不是我们所能接受的。停摆可能是几个礼拜，也可能是几个月。

yingyinNormal.en: If you're a HeForShe, and I'm assuming that you are because otherwise you'd be in somebody else's press conference right now, I'm here to ask you: What is the impact you can have? How? What? Where? When? And with whom?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你是HeForShe的支持者，我假定你们都是了，否则你们现在就在别人的新闻发布会上了，我想要问你的是你能有多大的影响力？以何种方式？何时？何地？与何人一道，产生何种影响？
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《艾玛·沃特森达沃斯世界经济论坛HeForShe演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: Some are great, and have a powerful impact on their audiences.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有的很棒，也对他们的听众有很大的影响力。

yingyinNormal.en: When something like the Blooming Onion hits big, the impact is felt all the way back to its source.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当像开花洋葱这样的东西出名，它的影响力能一直传导到原料产地。

yingyinNormal.en: Impact 10x10x10 is about concrete commitments to change, the visibility of these commitments and the measurability of them, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 影响力10x10x10为的是那些对做出改变脚踏实地的贡献，这些贡献能否眼见为实以及能否被量化。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《艾玛·沃特森达沃斯世界经济论坛HeForShe演讲》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the effect or influence of one person, thing, or action, on another

examination_example.sentence: The better you understand the cultural context, the more control you can have over your <highlight>impact</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你越了解文化背景，就越能控制自己的影响。

examination_example.sentence: Get clear on what <highlight>impact</highlight> you're hoping to have.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 弄清楚你希望产生什么样的影响。

examination_example.sentence: No matter how formal or informal the work environment, the way you present yourself has an <highlight>impact</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 无论工作环境是正式还是非正式，你展现自己的方式都会产生影响。

sense_info_list.en: come into forcibly contact with another object

examination_example.sentence: As such, they are key species for understanding and predicting <highlight>impacts</highlight> of global change on Antarctic and sub-Antarctic marine ecosystems.

examination_example.sentence: Although these may not seem like large effects, the <highlight>impact</highlight> of early attention problems continued throughout the children's academic careers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然这些影响看似不大，但早期注意力问题的影响贯穿了孩子们的整个学习生涯。

examination_example.sentence: Massive rubbish dumps and sprawling landfills constitute one of the more uncomfortable <highlight>impacts</highlight> that humans have on wildlife.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大量的垃圾场和不断扩张的垃圾填埋场是人类对野生动物造成的最令人不安的影响之一。

sense_info_list.en: the effect or influence of one person; thing; or action; on another

examination_example.sentence: It is electricity consumption by microwaves that has the biggest <highlight>impact</highlight> on the environmen.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 微波炉的电力消耗对环境影响最大。

examination_example.sentence: "Married women diagnosed with a serious health condition may find themselves struggling with the <highlight>impact</highlight> of their disease while also experiencing the stress of divorce, " said researcher Amelia Karraker.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究人员 Amelia Karraker 说：“被确诊身患重疾的已婚女性也许会发现自己在努力对抗疾病侵袭的同时，也在经历着离婚的压力。”

examination_example.sentence: Initiatives also include efforts to reduce its environmental <highlight>impact</highlight>, water consumption and materials used in packaging by 2025.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 举措还包括努力在2025年前减少其对环境的影响，用水量和包装材料的使用。

examination_example.sentence: Roads would be quieter, people safer. But we must also consider the <highlight>impact</highlight> of the new technology on those who now depend on driving for their livelihoods.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 道路将更加安静，人们将更加安全。但我们也必须考虑到新技术对现在依靠开车谋生的人的影响。

examination_example.sentence: Living in an urban area with green spaces has a long-lasting positive <highlight>impact</highlight> on people's mental well-being, a study has suggested.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一项研究表明，生活在绿色区域对人们的心理健康有着持久的积极影响。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the effect or influence of one person, thing, or action, on another

examination_example.sentence: After that, Orion wanted to make an even bigger <highlight>impact</highlight> (影响).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在那之后，猎户座想要产生更深刻的影响。

examination_example.sentence: Washing your hands with soap can have a huge <highlight>impact</highlight> on reducing (减少) the spread of diseases.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 用肥皂洗手可以大大减少疾病的传播的影响。
